# {{ name }} (Python WASM App)

This is a minimal Python WASM application scaffold.

- Default backend: wasi
- Optional backend: pyodide (add a label `backend:pyodide` to the target)
- Lockfile: uv.lock (importer-scoped)

## Usage

Build via planner-selected derivation (requires exported Buck graph):

```bash
node tools/buck/export-graph.ts
BUCK_TARGET=//apps/{{ name }}:{{ name }} nix build --impure -L --accept-flake-config '.#graph-generator-selected' --no-link
```

Run the tiny runner emitted by the WASM template:

```bash
OUT=$(BUCK_TARGET=//apps/{{ name }}:{{ name }} nix build --impure -L --accept-flake-config '.#graph-generator-selected' --print-out-paths)
node "$OUT/bin/run.mjs"
```


